subject: JUnit as Addin to JDeveloper 9i?
msgSnippet: Has anyone setup JUnit as an Addin to JDeveloper 9i?  The JDeveloper setup at www.junit.org appear to be for the prior version of JDeveloper (3.x) and does not
messageBody:
Has anyone setup JUnit as an Addin to JDeveloper 9i? The JDeveloper
setup at www.junit.org appear to be for the prior version of
JDeveloper (3.x) and does not work (for me at least) w/ the 9i
version. I can dig into it myself if no one has done so, but am
hoping that someone has already done this and can help me save some
time and effort (that really needs to go toward building and testing
my code... :-)

Thanks,

Jim
